                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Nivel 1-2 -->
                    <div class="level-card level-1">
                        <div class="card-badge highlight">‚öôÔ∏è INTERMEDIO</div>
                        <div class="icon-header">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined"
                                >handyman</span
